articles.author: CBS News
articles.title: European leaders, media stunned by JD Vance's speech - CBS News
articles.description: Vice President JD Vance stunned European leaders in Munich this week with a speech in which he painted a picture of European politics infected by media censorship and political correctness. Elizabeth Palmer has more.
